# 100% Free — No Paid Solutions

This app must remain **100% free** now and in the future.

## Do

- Prefer free tiers of services (Render free, Vercel free, Neon free, Brevo free).
- For local dev email: omit `BREVO_API_KEY` and log magic links / invite links to the API console.
- Use Brevo with a verified sender email (e.g. Gmail) — no custom domain purchase required.
- When a feature needs delivery to arbitrary emails, use Brevo or in-app link display — not paid domains.

## Do not

- Suggest buying domains, paid email plans, or any paid SaaS upgrade.
- Suggest services that require payment now or are likely to require payment later for this use case.
- Add dependencies with mandatory paid tiers for core flows (auth, invites, hosting, DB).

## Examples

```
❌ "Buy a domain and verify it in Resend"
❌ "Upgrade to a paid email plan"
✅ "Leave BREVO_API_KEY empty locally; copy links from the API terminal"
✅ "Verify your Gmail as a Brevo sender — free, sends to any recipient"
```
